name: Unreal Tournament 2004 (Includes MegaMap Pack)
author: noreply@schafhaupt.com
description:
Original developer: https://github.com/GFXSpeed/ut2004_pterodactyl

Modified by Trent

Now includes the megamap pack maps!

installation.script:
#!/bin/bash

echo "Installing pre-reqs"
apt update
apt install -y bzip2 curl tar

#download server files
echo "Downloading megapack"
curl -sSL -progress-bar -o ut2004_megapack.tar.bz2 https://github.com/liflg/ut2004.megapack-english/raw/master/ut2004_megapack.tar.bz2
echo "Downloading server files"
curl -sSL --progress-bar -o dedicated-server-3339-bonuspack.tar.gz https://s3.amazonaws.com/ut2004-files/dedicated-server-3339-bonuspack.tar.gz

#unpack
mkdir -p /mnt/server
mkdir -p /mnt/server/ut-server
tar -xjvf ut2004_megapack.tar.bz2 -C /mnt/server/ut-server/
tar -xzvf dedicated-server-3339-bonuspack.tar.gz --strip-components=1 -C /mnt/server/
cp -R /mnt/server/ut-server/* /mnt/server
rm -rf /mnt/server/ut-server
rm -rf mnt/server/System/UT2004.ini

#get setup files
echo "Downloading setup files"
curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/GFXSpeed/ut2004_pterodactyl/main/setup_files/UT2004.ini>> mnt/server/System/UT2004.ini
curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/trentnbauer/PelicanEggs/main/ut2004/start.sh>> mnt/server/start.sh\

echo "Generating cdkey file"
touch /mnt/server/System/cdkey

#set permissions
echo "Fixing permissions"
find /mnt/server/ -type d -exec chmod 755 {} +
find /mnt/server/ -type f -exec chmod 644 {} +
chmod +x /mnt/server/System/ucc-bin
chmod +x /mnt/server/start.sh

cd /mnt/server || exit

chown -R root:root /mnt

export HOME=/mnt/server

## install end
echo "-----------------------------------------"
echo "Installation completed..."
echo "-----------------------------------------"
